data.description: Welcome to this beautiful and tastefully remodeled home.  New modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite counter tops.  3 bedrooms on the main level, nice bathroom, good sized family room with wood burning fireplace in the lower level, tons of storage in this home, new windows and front door.  Awesome backyard with privacy fence, sprinkler system, huge concrete patio, fire pit area, storage shed and lots of space to play, garden and relax.
